{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"10409","heading":"Assessment reports","label":"10409 Assessment reports","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t34/stI/ch101/schXVII","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft34%2Fs10409","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","CodificationSection was formerly classified to , The Public Health and Welfare, prior to editorial reclassification and renumbering as this section.section 3796ee–8 of Title 42"],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Reports to Attorney General","label":"a Reports to Attorney General","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft34%2Fs10409%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"In general","label":"1 In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft34%2Fs10409%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Except as provided in paragraph (4), for each fiscal year for which a grant or subgrant is awarded under this subchapter, each State or specially qualified unit of local government that receives such a grant shall submit to the Attorney General a grant report, and each unit of local government that receives such a subgrant shall submit to the State a subgrant report, at such time and in such manner as the Attorney General may reasonably require.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Grant report","label":"2 Grant report","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft34%2Fs10409%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/a/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft34%2Fs10409%2Fa%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a summary of the activities carried out with such grant;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/a/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft34%2Fs10409%2Fa%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"if such activities included any subgrant, a summary of the activities carried out with each such subgrant; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/a/2/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft34%2Fs10409%2Fa%2F2%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"an assessment of the effectiveness of such activities on achieving the purposes of this subchapter.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":"Subgrant report","label":"3 Subgrant report","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/a/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft34%2Fs10409%2Fa%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/a/3/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/a/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft34%2Fs10409%2Fa%2F3%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a summary of the activities carried out with such subgrant; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/a/3/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/a/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft34%2Fs10409%2Fa%2F3%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"an assessment of the effectiveness of such activities on achieving the purposes of this subchapter.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":"Waivers","label":"4 Waivers","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/a/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft34%2Fs10409%2Fa%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/a/4/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/a/4","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft34%2Fs10409%2Fa%2F4%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the nature of the activities are such that assessing their effectiveness would not be practical or insightful;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/a/4/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/a/4","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft34%2Fs10409%2Fa%2F4%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the amount of the grant or subgrant is such that carrying out the assessment would not be an effective use of those amounts; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/a/4/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/a/4","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft34%2Fs10409%2Fa%2F4%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the resources available to the State or unit are such that carrying out the assessment would pose a financial hardship on the State or unit.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Reports to Congress","label":"b Reports to Congress","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft34%2Fs10409%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft34%2Fs10409%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a summary of the information provided under subsection (a);","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft34%2Fs10409%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"an assessment by the Attorney General of the grant program carried out under this subchapter; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/b/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t34/s10409/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft34%2Fs10409%2Fb%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"such other information as the Attorney General considers appropriate.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}
